data.description: Welcome to a new refurbished 2 flat units with all new interiors from the floor to the ceiling. Newly remodeled Kitchens with new kitchen counters and kitchen appliances. Newly remodeled bathrooms with new sinks and baths or showers for your liking. New carpets and flooring. We also installed new energy saving windows to keep those cold days outside. All the interior doors are new. A 2 car garage with great space. Huge back yard for you to relax in. Just mins away from shopping center and restaurants. Close enough to highways and main streets to get you to where you need to go.
